#. type: Plain text
#: ../../../../../doc/misc/message.texi:1283
msgid "As a final workaround, you can make the sign and encryption work in two steps; separately sign, then encrypt a message.  If you would like to change this behavior you can customize the @code{mml-signencrypt-style-alist} variable.  For example:"
