#. type: Plain text
#: ../../../../../doc/misc/message.texi:1304
msgid "By default, messages are encrypted to all recipients (@code{To}, @code{CC}, @code{BCC} headers).  Thus, you will not be able to decrypt your own messages.  To make sure that messages are also encrypted to your own key(s), several alternative solutions exist:"
